metadata.description:
**Attention**

If you own this NFT, please sign the Terms & Conditions located [here](https://lpr.remaster.io/contract/0x65a1F71dB66a7016d91f8C6d42A6a1A1E380a75B/1/true?Id=0&lic=-1) 

Crypt TV’s mission is to create iconic monsters.

Scamp is a collection of 666 monsters that give you specific IP rights from Crypt TV. Scamp is one of Crypt’s most beloved monsters and has been seen by millions of people. Scamp is a mischievous rascal… who knows what he will bring with him.

We hope you join us as we bring horror to this new frontier.

**Note:**

If there are licenses attached you will not be able to trade your NFT unless you sign.
